(SG-Å)[Ådmin] Dr.Rodney McKay: 

Welcome on my last Map Update, that's the final Version of Atlantis. I have little bugs on there pls ignore it and have fun. 

Features: 
The map is in "HDR" It plays by night 
You can switch the lights 
You can open/close the jumper bay door 
You can de-/activated the Charanktäne (all doors will be closed and locked) 
Big Atlantis (City) with flying Jumper (3D Skybox) 
There are many secrets on the map ( f.e Yanus Lab, ZPM Room...) 
Originale Atlantis DHD + Shield 
Original Sound's from the Movies 
Bomb A Zone = ZPM Room |Bomb B Zone = Chairroom 
T-Spawnpoint in the big Temple with 3 doors 1. Touch the door 2. Push the door 3. Acient console to open it Ct-Spawnpoint in Atlantis
